text: Apan dono toh first year se hi saath ro rhe hein bhai. Shuru se hi tera goal set tha, branch change krni hai, kr li usme. Phir yr aage khud hi mai busy rehne lg gya, meri hi galti thi time nhi de pya. But jb jb bhi exams ho, fest ho sath hi ghume. Intern time bhai tune hi sambhala mrko, lg toh jti hi yr mujhe bhi pta tha, but jo support tune diya diya uss time pe bhai lifetime nhi bhul skta. I know abhi tereko bhot si cheezein sort krni hai, but yr trust rkh sb sahi hoga, time lgta hai cheezon mein. Kabhi bhi kuch kaam hua tereko hi call krunga, ab toh direct tere ghar hi aa jaunga. Ek trip bhi kr lete hein jb tk tu India mein hai, kya pta baad mein tu mile na mile. Pichli trip toh epic thi bhai. Kya hi thand lgti thi tujhe, saare hi kaand tere saath hote the. Shashank ke nam pe ruk jta tha, company dene ke liye. Jld milte hein yr. All the Best bhai.
author: Ritesh  Kumar

text: Bhai apan shyd 2nd year mein mile the, but assignments ke liye kafi time saath gujra. ML toh epic tha, yaad hai woh raat ko roll lane ke liye ld rhe the apan sb, ram mn hi nhi rha tha. Uske baad south asia, crypto ... Mza aaya saath mein pr apna chess ka game reh gya yr, ik harunga but mza aayega usme bhi. Jld hi milte hein bhai, All the Best!!!

text: Bhai bina btaye kaise samaj jta hai tu meri problems? Mereko jaana h yr. Uss din bhi jb panelling thi, tu smaj gya. Jb bhi problems aayi, tu saath tha bhai. Pta nhi pr tu bhot jyada sympathetic hai. Emotinally tu jitna strong hai, utna maine kisi ko nhi dekha. Dost toh mera hai tu bhai bhot acha. Kitna hi time saath bitaya hai bhai. Last 2 mahine yaad hai tum aur dipak mereko bolte the krwa do, bhai mai nhi krta LOL. Pr alag famous ho gya tha mai. Cute th bhot ho tum, female following itni hai tumhri LOL,pr bhot saari stories jaani hai yr tumhari aadhi-adhoori pta hai.  Yeah wli trip jane ka bhot mn tha yr, but reasons the nhi ja pya. Koi aur pan bne toh jrur btana bhai. Aise hi smile rkte rehna yr. Ache lgte ho. All the best!!!
author: Ritesh  Kumar

text: Bhai IIT ki zindagi poori na hoti teri bina, you had been there whenever I was in trouble.(shayad tu hi panauti tha).Many a times kitne logon ki frustation tere upar nikli but you understood. Honestly, the day "jis din tum matlabi the" the patience and  bravery you faced all of it, DIL jeet liya bhai.I know tera circle bhot bda hai and people ignore ho jte hein but I am glad to be in your inner circle. Classes jne ki aadat tumhri wjah se hi chuti, dono ek dusre ko dekh kr sote rehte the üòÇ .   Location change ho jye bhai ksi ki bhi , preferably teri üòõ, wrna aage ke assignment  merese toh nhi hone wle. Aur haan treat ab toh de de bhai.
author: Ritesh  Kumar

text: Bhai kb shuruaat hui mujhe exact toh nhi yaad, pr mishra ne hi milwya hoga.1st year mein km  hi mile the hum  log, batch bhi alag tha upar se bhot sunn rkha tha ki AIR 10 ANANY SHARMA. PR 2nd year se toh poora time saath hi beeta. Assignment ki BT se lekr Antaragini ki DJ nights tk, hr jgah saath the. M thoda isloated rehna hi pasand krta tha, shd isliye itna ghum nhi paaye bahar saath. Jb time aaya mera toh corona hi sb gdbd kr gya. Phir bhi jo bhi time tha, hmesha yaad rhega bhai. Chaapu tu sbke liye hoga, mere liye toh bhai pehle hai. Abhi bhale hi alag alag raaste ho apan teeno ki, pr manzil ek hi hogi mereko pta hai. Apan teeno ki hi degree shyd ek dusre ki bina poori na ho pti. Kaash thoda time aur mil paata apan logon ko saath mein. Kuch saalon ki baat hai, phir sath hi ayenge. I had the best moment of IITk with you, jab hum dono ne woh ICPC wla dusra sawaal kiya tha. Aur jb 12 wrong attempt k baad sahi ho gya tha, jitni joor se chillaye the RM mein. 5 minute tk gale lge rhe the bhai. Roj flex krte the phir LOL.Bhai uss din alag feel aayi thi. Kitne assignment kitini BT inn salon mein pr bhai tum dono ka saath nhi hota mai nhi kr pata. Poems mst likhta hai bhai, continue krna. Itne time mein bhi apni saath mein kitni kam photos hein, pr yaadein bhot hein. Enjoy krna bhai Singapore mein. Mereko bhi casino ghumana. Jld hi trading shuru krenge. Jld milte hein bhai.
author: Ritesh  Kumar

text: Bhai apni toh bhot yaadein hein, First summer mein batti wle project(jo kbhi poora nhi ho pya) se lekr CS core team tk. Apan kafi time tk saath rhe. I think tum kafi effort marte ho , jahan bhi rehte ho. Project mein bhi bhai, tum kafi kaam krte the, apni CS team ki toh jaan the hi tum. Kafi ache handle krte the tum  cheezon ko. Kafi jldi connect kr lete ho tum logon se.Tumhare kisse sune the jb OAT mein toh bhai alag level respect bdh gyi thi. Maine apni saari problems tumse share krta tha, chahe acds ki ya life ki aur tensions(tum smaj gye hoge) but tum hmsha sunte, kafi connected feel krta tha bhai terese. Apan kafi ache dost bn gye the,  aage bhi pareshan krta rhunga bhai.Bhot kuch seekhna hai waise toh tumse pr usme abhi time hai. All the Best bhai placements ke liye, chapne wle ho tum ,bs confidence rkhna. Jld hi milenge.All the best!!!
author: Ritesh  Kumar

text: DOST, sahi mein ache dost ho yr tum. First year mein ho ache dost bn gye the apan. Hagge ke udhar kuch logon se hi baat hoti thi pehle. Aakhiri sem mein Financial tumne hi bachaya hai yr. Padhai toh apni jagah, anataragini mein I-Card wla kaand yaad hai? Kitna sunaya tha SIS ne. Alag hi time tha woh bhi. Shayad apni last antaragini.Di ke bhot ache ho bhai tum. Tumse baat krte krte kb time nikal jta hai pta hi nhi chlta. Touch mein rehna dost. All the best!!!
author: Ritesh  Kumar

text:
Hey ayush,

text: Bhai 1st summer mein mile the bhai. Roj kya masti krte the. Chess, football, swimming aur pta nhi kya kya... All rounder ho bhai tum. Woh BBQ wli bet toh hmesha yaad rhegi. Tumri victory celebration mein biryani. Uske baad itne assignments, itna football, itne patte khele. Bhot time saath gujra.Dance reh gya bhai bs terese seekhna. Aise hi videos ba kr daalte rehna. Last mein yr aate aate kitna senti ho gye the yr. Bhai bhot acha dost hai tu, jb bhi college ki yaad ayegi tu hmesha yaad ayega. Tu jaisa bhi hai , mst hai. Chaapte rehna life mein!!!!
author: Ritesh  Kumar

text: First year se jyada change aaya nhi yr tere mein. Wohi bholi shakal, gurukul wali harkate. Thoda bolna chalu kr de bhai. Gym jane ka abhi bhi soch hi rha hai, ya gya bhi hai? @nd year ke baad se yr department alag ho gye apne phir time nhi mila saath. Pr bhai tune jo meri DOAA mein pic li thi woh aaj bhi spam ke kaam aa rhi logon ke. Baburao wli video yaad hai jo apan ne kapurwan ke saath bnayi thi? Ek br yaad hai mere birthday se pehle cylce pe itni dur nikal gye the, kitna sunaya tha sabne. Mst din the bhai. Gamer toh alag level hai bhai tu. Tere dimag ek game zone bn chuka hai .Aise hi cheat-codes crak krta reh. All the best bhai aage ke liye!!!
author: Ritesh  Kumar

text: Bhai 1st summer mein pehli baar tumse mile. Kya epic time tha bhai. Mishra ka saara pol khla tum. ATP ki equation solve ki. Phir mishra se bachne ke liye hum log tere room chal jte the. Uske baad se toh bhai regularly milte the, assignment mein tum bhot help kiya. Tumare birthday pr hum log hr br GPL lene aa jte the. Tumhara hall dur tha yr, Hall 2 rehta na tumhra toh bhot mza aata. Phir bhi bhai saath bhut mze kiye. aakhiri 2 mahine toh pta nhi tum badal mein kya bna rhe the. Mehnati toh hai bs kismat achi nhi h. lady luch chaiye tumko, ladies' nhi. Milte rhenge bhai, kabhi ghumne ka plan bne saath toh mza hi a jyega. All the best bhai!!!
author: Ritesh  Kumar

text:
"Bhai DS ka assignment krna hai, 12 bje deadline hai". Shyd mile hum tumse pehle bhi honge, pr baatein toh yahi se chalu hui. Tumhre campus ka shyd best time chal rha tha. Shashank nhi hota toh shyd hum tumko kbhi jan bhi nhi paate. Yaad hai ek raat ko baat kr rhe the, aur mishra ek kutte ke saath hi so gya tha.  Pichla ek saal toh shyd m sahi m depress ho jta, agar roj itna time pass nhi krte. Shyd roj 6-7 ghante apne video call pr hi nikalte the, pta nhi kya hi discussion chalta tha. Yaad hai tumse aur shashank se maine sorry post krwaya tha instagram pe,jb tum log call pr nhi aaye the. Aakhiri 2 mahine toh campus mein alag hi mze the.Yahan aa kr maine shyd tumhre chqr mein itni cheezein try kr li, ki poora campus dealer smjne lg gya tha mrko. Alag mze the uske bhi. Dil ka sahi mein bhot acha hai bhai tu, pichle ek saal mein logon se kitna kuch suna especially placement times, I know tune apni traf se poori koshish ki.Bhot bura lgta h, jb log SPO team aur tum logon ko blame krte hein, tum sb logon ne genuinely bhot acha kaam kiya hai aur pichle saalon ki teams se bhot better kiya hai.Life bhot bdi h, tujhe bhot aage jna h life mein choti- choti problems se pareshan mt hua kr. Dono ki location bhale hi alag ho, pr tujhe toh pta hi h, apan log virtually jitna touch mein rehte hein utna toh shyd log saath reh kr bhi ek dusre ko nhi jaante honge.Aur haan saari bhijwa dena, nhi toh rkhe rkhe kharab ho jygi,photo hai abhi bhi mere pass.

text: Mere CS ke shyd pehle dost the tum. Tumse kaafi jldi connect kr lia tha maine, jo shyd mai bhot logon se nhi kr pata. PHY103 ki classes kya sahi handle krte the tum. Tumhre aur ashish ke hi itne sahi efforts the ki hum logon ne classes ki condition itni sahi kr li thi. Maine mails mein kitni gdbd ki thi LOL, ek br toh corrected mail  hi glat bhej diya tha, pr tum log sambla lete the. 3rd year mein kitni time saath bitaya, kitni hi saari yaadein hein. Bs yr jb masti ka time aaya, treats ka, toh corona ho gya. Aur haan jo paise humne kamaye(laakhon ka maal tha) usse ek trip toh sponsor ho hi jygi. Chlte hein khin.  Yr waise tum aur rahul na hote toh m placement mein itna acha kabhi nhi kr pta, mera aur P Singh ki bhot help hui. Hmesha motivate kiya. Full package hai bhai tu, helpful, supportive, chaapu, spammer, popular, bs ek gf bna le mn lga rhega LOL. Delhi jld hi aata hu tere hi pas rhunga. Last trip miss krne ka bhot dukh tha yr, pr kuch personnel reasons the nhi ja pya. Phir kbhi plan bnao toh jrur mrko bhi lena. Keep spamming,dipuk!!!!

text: Bhai kahan se shuru krun. Tereko shyd yaad na ho , pehli baar tu mila tha jb tu E-Cell ke event ke liye sbko bulane aaya tha. Phir ek do br tere room pe mila, kya safai rkhta tha bhai tu. First summers se toh bhai saath  hi rhe. Woh summer kya epic tha. Mai bahar jyada nhi jta tha, isliye saath bhot photos nhi hai yr, but memories bhot hein. Hr course se related itni hein ki kya btaun. Baswana sir wla toh yaad hi hoga.OS yaad hai tu roj uthane aata tha aur hum soe reh jte the.  Last year maien socha tha yr ghumenge pr kya hi ho gya. Phir bhi last mein tum logon ne saare mze krwa hi diye. Bhot ache din the yr, yeah akhiri ke 1-2 mahine campus mein.  Ek GOA trip krni hai bhai saath mein, jb bhi time mile. Tere aur tere bhai mein pehchana mushkil h bhai. Jld hi milte hein yr.  All the best!!!
